Summary: 2 oval white glowing ships and one unknown.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was 16 visiting my aunt with my folks .Around 1700 or so I went out side to enjoy the night sky as I look up I saw two oval shape objects space apart fly straigh up, they disappeared and reappeared further up i brought my folks out to watch as they step out they saw the same obejects as i did as they did the same thing again were going straight up and disappeared from view ,they went inside and I stayed looking at the night sky for a few more mins. As I turn around to go inside there was a object over the house ,it wasnt a ufo but one of our own space craft,I look at it in detail as it had a black tip long and white with checkers circling the body of the rocket. The ship look like it was burning at the end I notice flames. it was the leaght of my aunts house but not its true size. And stars in the back ground it look to be burning up. I stood in awe just looking at it.I was not scared at all ,But felt they were telling me they were watching us . I look around but there was nothing around me nor did the ufo or the craft i was looking make any noise. I stood there until it disappeared. And I went inside and told everyone what I saw. Till this day I have search the net for this aircraft I saw I have yet to find it. I really need to know if anyone else has seen this or know of this ship I saw. I have seen my share of ufo from Tenn. to Fla. I feel this is as close of a encounter I wish to ever get with one.And still wish why they showed it to me.I have question but never recieved answers. Can you give me any thing at all!?
